<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146176>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–18. Female accessory sclerite (Figs 8, 10–16, 18) and spermatheca (Figs 9, 17) of Omalium: 8–9—O. acutangulum, 10—O. amicorum, 11—O. amplissimum, 12—O. bilobum, 13—O. alticola, 14—O.beesoni, 15—O. altivagans, 16–17—O. marginatum, 18—O. scapulare. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146176/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146208>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56–58. Habitus of Omalium: 56—O. marginatum (holotype), 57—O. scapulare (Nepal, Bagmati), 58—O. angustissimum (holotype). Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146208/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146212>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62–64. Aedeagus of Omalium scapulare (Nepal: Bagmati): 62—aedeagus, parameral view, 63—aedeagus, lateral view, 64—median lobe, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146214>
